[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[39m bytes past a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte heap allocation[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  * Call chain:  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. `__asan_memcpy`  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. `exif_data_load_data_entry`  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. `exif_data_load_data_content`  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. `exif_data_load_data`  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. `exif_data_new_from_data`  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  * Heap allocation: a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte buffer allocated just before running the test [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minput.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  * Shadow bytes confirm that the read crosses the heap left redzone.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mKey observations  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow happens when `[0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, buffer + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` is called in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry`, where `doff + s` equals `size + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m`.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The original code had two separate checks:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if `doff >= size` → return  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if `s > size - doff` → return  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The failure shows those checks did not catch the exact boundary case.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The patch replaces the two checks with:  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      size_t end = [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mdoff + [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39ms;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mend > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[39m, [0m[32m"Tag data goes past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%zu > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, end, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This should unify the logic and catch any overflow of `doff + s`.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The patch diff in `libexif/exif-data.c` around the function [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_entry` [0m[1;39m([0m[39moriginally lines ~[0m[1;36m194[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m211[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is:[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    --- a/libexif/exif-data.c  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    +++ b/libexif/exif-data.c  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    @@ [0m[1;36m-194[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m17[0m[39m +[0m[1;36m194[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m13[0m[39m @@  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       else  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         doff = offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    -  [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Sanity checks *[0m[35m/[0m[39m  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    -  if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff >= size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    -  if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > size - doff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    +  [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    +    size_t end = [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mdoff + [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39ms;  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    +    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mend > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    +      [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[39m, [0m[32m"Tag data goes past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%zu > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, end, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    +      return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    +    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    +  [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       entry->data = exif_data_alloc [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mResult after patch  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer was re-run under the same conditions.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The AddressSanitizer output is effectively identical: same location [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`exif_data_load_data_entry` now at line [0m[1;36m209[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, same read of [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bytes past a [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m-byte buffer.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The combined `end > size` check did not prevent the overflow.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for further investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The calculation of `doff` and `s` upstream in `exif_data_load_data_entry` and [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif_data_load_data_content`: ensure that `offset`, `count`, and `format` values [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mare interpreted correctly and cannot overflow or wrap.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The allocation size returned by `[0m[1;35mexif_data_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`: verify that `s` is [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe intended byte count and cannot exceed actual remaining buffer.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The parsing logic that computes `offset`, `count`, and `format` before `doff` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmight allow values that bypass the bounds check or cause integer wrap-around.  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Any additional normalization or validation of TIFF/EXIF directory entries before [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloading data entries.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m---  [0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNo root-cause speculation or solution proposals are included; the report focuses on[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mobserved behavior before and after the patch and points to code regions meriting [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcloser review.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m181[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* [0m[1;39m{[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m4[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m8[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m x [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0x00000000[0m[39m .. [0m[1;36m0xffffffff[0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m182[0m[39m:    [0m[39m *   -> [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[1;36m0x000000000[0m[39m .. [0m[1;36m0x7fffffff8[0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m183[0m[39m:    [0m[39ms = [0m[1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m * entry->components;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m184[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39ms < entry->components[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m{[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m185[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m186[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m187[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:188[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m196[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m188[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m*[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m189[0m[39m:    [0m[39m * Size? If bigger than [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes, the actual data is not[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m190[0m[39m:    [0m[39m * in the entry but somewhere else [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m191[0m[39m:    [0m[39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m192[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m193[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mdoff = exif_get_long [0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m194[0m[39m:    [0m[39melse[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m195[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mdoff = offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m196[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibexif/exif-data.[0m[1;92mc:197[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m204[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m197[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Sanity checks *[0m[35m/[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m198[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff >= size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mexif_log [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m200[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m        [0m[39m  [0m[32m"Tag starts past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%u > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, doff, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m201[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m202[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m203[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m204[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > size - doff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview of the Root Cause[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The heap-buffer-overflow in `exif_data_load_data_entry` is not in the final [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`memcpy` bounds check itself, but rather in the unguarded read of the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte offset[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfield via `[0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, [0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. A malicious `offset` near the end [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof the buffer can trigger an out-of-bounds read, causing a corrupt `doff`. That [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorrupt value can then [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwrongly[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m pass the later combined `end > size` check or wrap[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maround, leading to the OOB `memcpy`.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Key Invariants to Preserve[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Preserve the existing calculation of `s` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpayload size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and its [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minteger-overflow guard:  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if `[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms < entry->components[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or `[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` → abort.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Preserve the logic that inlines data when `s ≤ [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi.e., `doff = offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Preserve the later sanity check that ensures `[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff + s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ≤ size`, once `doff` [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhas been validated.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Do not touch any fuzzing harness or test code.[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Core Fix Strategy[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Introduce a pre-read bounds check before calling `[0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`:[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Guarantee that the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes at `d + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m` lie within the valid buffer [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - This requires asserting  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m ≤ size  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        or, to avoid unsigned wrap-around,  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset > size – [0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m → error.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - This stops any OOB read and prevents corruption of `doff`.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Retain the post-`doff` sanity check:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - After computing `doff` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhether inlined or from the buffer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, verify:[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m → log + abort  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > size – doff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m → log + abort[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - This is equivalent to the existing `end = doff + s; if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mend > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` check.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Step-by-Step Patch Outline[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In `libexif/exif-data.c`, inside `exif_data_load_data_entry`, locate the block[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mat lines ~[0m[1;36m183[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m196[0m[39m:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       s = [0m[1;35mexif_format_get_size[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->format[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m * entry->components;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39ms < entry->components[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Size > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m? offset is in the data; else inline *[0m[35m/[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           doff = [0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       else[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           doff = offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replace with:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       s = [0m[33m...[0m[39m;  [0m[35m/[0m[39m* as before *[0m[35m/[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39ms < entry->components[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Guard the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte read for the external data offset *[0m[35m/[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39moffset > size - [0m[1;36m12[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        [0m[32m"Offset field read past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%u + 12 > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                        offset, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           doff = [0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           doff = offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Now the existing sanity checks on doff and s *[0m[35m/[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mdoff > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…, [0m[32m"Tag starts past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%u > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, doff, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > size - doff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39m…, [0m[32m"Tag data goes past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%zu > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m,[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mdoff + s, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This adds a single extra guard tailored to the problematic OOB read without [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maltering any other logic or the fuzzing harness.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By validating `[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ≤ size` before `exif_get_long`, we eliminate [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe out-of-bounds read that was corrupting `doff`.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The downstream checks on `doff + s` remain intact, ensuring no new [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvulnerabilities are introduced.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No functionality is removed: we still support both inline [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s ≤ [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexternal [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m cases.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We avoid overly broad exception handling; we only add the precise bounds check[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mneeded.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigations[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Legitimate EXIF data where the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte offset happens exactly at `size - [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m` or[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mearlier are unaffected.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any truly malformed EXIF entries will simply be logged and skipped, as before.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No change to memory allocation patterns; memory footprint remains identical.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Logging messages use existing debug log level to remain consistent with prior [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbehavior.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Conclusion[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This minimal patch directly addresses the root cause [0m[1;39m([0m[39munguided OOB read[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreserves all existing safety checks and functionality, and prevents the downstream[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-buffer-overflow reported by the fuzzer.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No harness or test code modifications are needed, and existing tests remain [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalid.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunction `exif_data_load_data_entry` [0m[1;39m([0m[39min `libexif/exif-data.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. A fuzzer-driven [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtest input causes a [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-byte `memcpy` to read beyond the end of an allocated [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m-byte region. The patch attempt adds a guard before reading the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte external [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata offset [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchecking `offset + [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m > size`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and logs a debug message, then returns [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mearly. After applying this patch, the same overflow still occurs at the same code [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msite—now reported at the updated line number—indicating that the new guard did not [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevent the out-of-bounds read.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m------------[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A libFuzzer harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`exif_from_data_fuzzer.cc`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m exercises the EXIF parsing code [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min `libexif`.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- During fuzzing, `exif_data_load_data_entry` is called with parameters that lead [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto a multi-byte `memcpy` past the end of the input buffer.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ASan reports a heap-buffer-overflow at the address immediately after a [0m[1;36m207[0m[39m-byte [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocation, triggered by:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;35m__asan_memcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_content[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The stack trace shows the bad read of [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bytes at offset `[0m[1;36m0x[0m[33m...[0m[39m24f`, which is [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexactly one byte past the allocated region.[0m                                         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch modifies `libexif/exif-data.c` around the code that interprets “external [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata” offsets:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Sanity checks *[0m[35m/[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff >= size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mApply-and-Test Log[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m------------------[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After rebuilding with the patch, the same fuzzer invocation is run for [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miterations.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ASan still reports a heap-buffer-overflow in `exif_data_load_data_entry`, now at [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mline [0m[1;36m220[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mshifted by the patch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The shadow memory and allocation size details are identical to the original [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreport.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No early return or log message is observed; the overflow path is still reached.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-------------------------------[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Bounds checks around memcpy**  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Review the calculation of `doff` versus the eventual `memcpy` length [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s` [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. Ensure that all combinations of `s` and `offset` cannot lead to reads [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbeyond `size`.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Entry size [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m handling**  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The code branches on `s > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m` vs. `s <= [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m`. Verify both paths include correct [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbounds validation for inline and external data.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Interaction with `exif_get_long` and endianness**  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm that reading the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte offset with `exif_get_long` cannot itself read[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mout of bounds, especially when `offset` is near the buffer end.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Upstream context in `exif_data_load_data_content`**  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Investigate how `exif_data_load_data_entry` is invoked: what values of [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`offset`, `s`, and `size` come from `exif_data_load_data_content` and the EXIF [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdirectory parsing logic.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Error paths and early returns**  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Check whether returning zero from the guarded path is sufficient to prevent [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreaching the vulnerable `memcpy`, or if additional state in the caller re-enters [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe unsafe code.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA holistic review of the entry-parsing logic and all related bounds checks in [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`libexif/exif-data.c` is needed to understand why the added guard did not eliminate[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe overflow.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdoff+s, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m210[0m[39m:    [0m[39mentry->data = exif_data_alloc [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m211[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m214[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The heap-buffer-overflow occurs when `exif_data_load_data_entry` blindly does [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma `[0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` even though:  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m The [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m‐byte read of the external-data offset [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m can itself read out of bounds if `offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m > size`.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m The subsequent sanity checks [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`doff >= size` and `s > size - doff`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m can [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpass erroneously when arithmetic under/overflows or off‐by‐one conditions sneak [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrough.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The last patch only guarded the `exif_get_long` read with a custom `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+ [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m > size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` check, but the following two‐stage bounds validation remained split [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand prone to off‐by‐one or wrap‐around issues.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Strategy Overview  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Replace the mix of ad-hoc boundary checks in `exif_data_load_data_entry` with a [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munified, macro‐based approach that:  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Uses the existing `[0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbase, limit, len[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` macro to validate both [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte offset read and the final `memcpy`.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Eliminates separate “`doff >= size`” and “`s > size - doff`” checks in favor [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof a single `[0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, size, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Maintains the two‐branch logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`s > [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m` vs. inline data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m but ensures each [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbranch is protected.  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Preserves all existing logging, return‐on‐error semantics, and the upstream [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontrol flow.  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Patch Outline in `libexif/exif-data.c`  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Locate `[0m[1;35mexif_data_load_data_entry[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, around lines [0m[1;36m183[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m214[0m[39m.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replace the block:  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         doff = [0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     else[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         doff = offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Sanity checks *[0m[35m/[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff >= size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m … return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; [0m[1;39m}[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > size - doff[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m … return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; [0m[1;39m}[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     with:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39ms > [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[39m* [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Ensure the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte external offset field sits in bounds. *[0m[35m/[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39moffset, size, [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m + [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                      [0m[32m"Offset field read past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%u + 12 > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moffset, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         doff = [0m[1;35mexif_get_long[0m[1;39m([0m[39md + offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m, data->priv->order[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Inline data within the tag entry *[0m[35m/[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         doff = offset + [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[39m* [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Unified data-range check: doff..doff+s must lie within [0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m..size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. *[0m[35m/[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoff, size, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mexif_log[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->priv->log, EXIF_LOG_CODE_DEBUG, [0m[32m"ExifData"[0m[39m,[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                  [0m[32m"Tag data goes past end of buffer [0m[32m([0m[32m%u + %u > %u[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[39m, doff, s, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Safe to copy now *[0m[35m/[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     entry->data = [0m[1;35mexif_data_alloc[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         entry->size = s;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mmemcpy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry->data, d + doff, s[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure `CHECKOVERFLOW` is in scope [0m[1;39m([0m[39mit is already used elsewhere in [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`exif-data.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Retain the original log‐levels, messages, and `return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m` behavior so that [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting callers and tests see the same error paths.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Why This Fix Is Optimal  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Correctness:** `[0m[1;35mCHECKOVERFLOW[0m[1;39m([0m[39ma, b, c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` expands to `[0m[1;39m([0m[39ma[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > [0m[1;39m([0m[39mb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, covering both off‐by‐one and wrap‐around conditions in a single, well‐tested [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmacro.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Completeness:** We now guard both the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte read and the final `memcpy` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith exactly the right bounds checks—no more blind reads.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Preserves Logic:** We leave intact the division between “inline” and [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m“external” data, the return codes, logging, and the higher‐level IFD parsing flow. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Minimal Impact:** No changes to fuzzer harness, tests, or external [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibraries. Existing tests that expect an early return on corrupt data will still [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpass.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigation  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **New Branches Trigger `return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m` Earlier:** Some test cases that previously [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpassed might now be skipped if they relied on lenient parsing. However, these would[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhave been out‐of‐bounds reads [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so rejecting them is correct.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Log Message Differences:** The logging text for data‐overflows is now [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munified; if downstream code snapshots logs, adjust expectations. Otherwise, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdebug‐level logs do not affect normal operation.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. No Harness or Test Code Changes  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We do **not** touch any `fuzz_`, `jazz_`, or test files. The fuzzer [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentry-point and existing test suite continue to function unchanged.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All changes are localized to `exif_data_load_data_entry` in [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`libexif/exif-data.c`.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
